channel.title: What kind of women do you go after
channel.description:
So moparscapians
what kind of women do you like to try and get?
I personaly would love one that is completly independant. One that i know wont be mooching off me simply because shes a woman. One that is with me, not cause she needs me, but just because she wants me.
however despite what i want, i always seem to be drawn towards asking out the emotionaly broken women. The ones that fall completly and desperatly in love within minuits of talking to you, sleep with you once and decide your everything in the world to them. While fun, those kinda women get very very boring, very very fast. No challenge whatsoever.
